      "content": "I hear you on the research aspects, but it feels like you're almost dismissive of the whole perspective. To you, is the \"tough on crime\" approach just fundamentally flawed or even harmful, or do you think there's a legitimate way to combine strict enforcement with those social programs you mentioned?",
